---
// Intron Bio - Homepage
// 采用 Astro + Tailwind CSS 驱动
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="zh-CN" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>上海内含子生物科技 | Intron Bio - 领先的分子生物学技术咨询</title>
    <meta name="description" content="上海内含子生物科技有限公司，专注于分子生物学技术咨询、生物计算与 AI 工作流，为尖端生命科学研究提供智能化解决方案。" />
  </head>
  
  <body class="bg-[#020617] text-slate-200 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-cyan-500/30">
    
    <div class="fixed inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -top-[10%] -left-[10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] rounded-full bg-cyan-900/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-[20%] -right-[10%] w-[30%] h-[50%] rounded-full bg-indigo-900/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      
      <header class="flex justify-between items-center py-10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-cyan-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black text-xs">IB</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white">
            INTRON BIO <span class="hidden md:inline text-slate-500 font-medium ml-1">内含子生物</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-10 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">
          <a href="#services" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Services / 业务</a>
          <a href="#expertise" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Expertise / 核心</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors border border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-cyan-400">Contact / 联系</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main class="py-20 md:py-32">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-full text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-400 mb-8 bg-cyan-500/5">
            Molecular intelligence & Consulting
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-10 tracking-tight text-white">
            Decoding <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-indigo-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Molecular</span><br />
            Complexity.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-light">
            我们致力于解析生命底层的复杂逻辑。通过智能化的分子技术咨询与 AI 辅助分析，协助科研团队跨越从实验设计到机制验证的鸿沟。
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 flex gap-6">
            <a href="#services" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all">开始技术咨询</a>
            <a href="#expertise" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-sm border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 transition-all">探索核心能力</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>

      <section id="services" class="py-24 border-t border-slate-900">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          
          <div class="group">
            <div class="mb-6 w-12 h-[2px] bg-cyan-500 group-hover:w-24 transition-all"></div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white italic">01. 分子生物学技术咨询</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
              针对复杂的科研课题，提供深度的实验体系优化咨询。涵盖遗传编码探针的动力学模拟、亚细胞定位机制解析、以及活体成像方案的闭环验证，确保研究路径的高效与严谨。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="mb-6 w-12 h-[2px] bg-indigo-500 group-hover:w-24 transition-all"></div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white italic">02. 生物计算与 AI 工作流</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
              利用 AI 基础软件开发能力，为实验室定制高通量的图像处理插件与生物信息工作流。将复杂的数据处理自动化，从噪声中精准提取生物学信号。
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="expertise" class="py-24 bg-slate-900/30 rounded-[3rem] px-8 md:px-16 border border-white/5">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-center text-slate-500 mb-16">Our Expertise / 核心技术栈</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-400 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Probe Design</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">探针设计与验证</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-400 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Bio-Imaging</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">生物影像解析</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-400 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">AI Plugins</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">AI 插件定制</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-cyan-400 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Mechanism</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">底层机制论证</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer id="contact" class="py-24 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">开启您的智能科研之旅</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-12 italic text-lg">“Intron: The essential information within the code.”</p>
          <div class="text-slate-500 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <p>内含子生物科技(上海)有限公司</p>
            <p>Intron Biotechnology (Shanghai) Co., Ltd.</p>
            <p class="pt-6 font-mono text-cyan-500/70 select-all">sale@intronbio.tech   </p>
            <p class="pt-6 font-mono text-cyan-500/70 select-all">+86 17501621170</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-24 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-700">
          &copy; 2026 INTRON BIO. All Rights Reserved.
        </div>
      </footer>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>